Aroma of roasted malts, not overpowering smoke aroma. Black appearance with a thin tan creamy head. light sweetness, very bitter, full body, oily feel, thick feel, bitter, long finish. Very tasty beer dor a cold winter night.
From a can, into a tulip glass. Nice creamy head Aroma of burnt coffee. Taste of watery, burnt coffee.
